  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>When Ed accepted the challenge of surviving exactly 20 days and 20 nights in The Demonic Conveyor Belt (D.C.B), he thought his Elite Mastery Professor had been exaggerating that it was 'the most feared dungeon of all'. This thought quickly disappeared into the fog surrounding him, when he passed through the gates of the dungeon to find the largest eyeball he'd ever seen. Would he forever remain just Ed, or could he become Talent Ed? </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Talented</strong> is an arcade roguelite shoot 'em up with randomly generated skill trees. Survive 20 nights and defeat the dungeon to unlock all six classes, each with unlockable talents, abilities and challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Send a hail of arrows, conjure powerful spells, brew unique potions, or call upon an army of snails to hold back the demons. The possibilities are endless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/00da2f50c68c754c6a2cd6f18efff313.avif?t=1756725642\" width=617 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/a3580f401cd5d0175a0afea90a28283c.poster.avif?t=1756725642\" width=618 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/a3580f401cd5d0175a0afea90a28283c.webm?t=1756725642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/a3580f401cd5d0175a0afea90a28283c.mp4?t=1756725642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft your own builds, with over 500 Talents to learn</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obliterate your foes, with over 100 abilities</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a new talent tree every run with randomly generated skill trees</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go Endless and push your builds to their limit</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/09418ec4f388d033525aa504746a65bf.poster.avif?t=1756725642\" width=630 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/09418ec4f388d033525aa504746a65bf.webm?t=1756725642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/09418ec4f388d033525aa504746a65bf.mp4?t=1756725642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master six classes, each with its own playstyle </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customise your character's loadout with class specific traits and skins </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself, with 25 mastery levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore new ways to play, with 10 challenges per class</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>When Ed accepted the challenge of surviving exactly 20 days and 20 nights in The Demonic Conveyor Belt (D.C.B), he thought his Elite Mastery Professor had been exaggerating that it was 'the most feared dungeon of all'. This thought quickly disappeared into the fog surrounding him, when he passed through the gates of the dungeon to find the largest eyeball he'd ever seen. Would he forever remain just Ed, or could he become Talent Ed? </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Talented</strong> is an arcade roguelite shoot 'em up with randomly generated skill trees. Survive 20 nights and defeat the dungeon to unlock all six classes, each with unlockable talents, abilities and challenges. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Send a hail of arrows, conjure powerful spells, brew unique potions, or call upon an army of snails to hold back the demons. The possibilities are endless.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/00da2f50c68c754c6a2cd6f18efff313.avif?t=1756725642\" width=617 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/a3580f401cd5d0175a0afea90a28283c.poster.avif?t=1756725642\" width=618 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/a3580f401cd5d0175a0afea90a28283c.webm?t=1756725642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2435090/extras/a3580f401cd5d0175a0afea90a28283c.mp4?t=1756725642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul clas